{"id":1087351909,"question_id":3106,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"7 months, 2 weeks","timestamp":1698647765,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"244 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/1087351909/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Length of the Longest Subsequence That Sums to Target","memory":"55.8 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    public int lengthOfLongestSubsequence(List<Integer> nums, int target) {\n        int siz = nums.size();\n\n        int[][] dp = new int[siz+1][target+1]; //看過i個數字後 能夠最長的subseq 組成target\n        for(int[] d : dp){\n            Arrays.fill(d, -1);\n        } \n\n        for(int i=0; i<siz; i++){\n            dp[i][0]=0;\n        }\n\n\n\n        for(int i=1; i<=siz; i++){\n            for(int j=1; j<=target; j++){\n\n                dp[i][j]=dp[i-1][j];\n\n                if(j-nums.get(i-1)>=0 && dp[i-1][j-nums.get(i-1)]!=-1){\n                    dp[i][j] = Math.max(dp[i][j], 1 + dp[i-1][j-nums.get(i-1)]);\n                }\n            }\n        }\n\n        return dp[siz][target]==0 ? -1 : dp[siz][target];\n\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"length-of-the-longest-subsequence-that-sums-to-target","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
